Class PddlType

    com.hp.hpl.jena.datatypes.RDFDatatype

    public class PddlType
extends com.hp.hpl.jena.datatypes.BaseDatatype
    PddlType is an extension type for dealing with Literals capturing PDDL expressions. This type is only necessary for handling the OWL-S descriptions part of OWL-S TC4
    Since:
    17/07/2013
    Author:
    Carlos Pedrinaci (KMi - The Open University)
